IONLGLDOAJL: When the active character triggers Frozen, Vaporize, or Electro-Charged reaction, the affected opponents will unleash a shockwave that deals Physical DMG within a certain AoE.
When the active character's Normal, Charged, or Plunging Attack hits an opponent, the opponent hit will unleash a shockwave that randomly deals Pyro or Electro DMG within a certain AoE.
When the active character triggers Swirl reaction, the affected opponents will unleash a shockwave that deals Physical DMG within a certain AoE.
When the active character defeats an opponent, a shockwave will be unleashed around the character and deal Dendro DMG within a certain AoE.
